>
  <p data-en={'This Cookie Policy explains how BiasharaPOS uses cookies and similar technologies on our website and application. It should be read together with our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.'} data-sw={'Sera hii ya Cookie inaeleza jinsi BiasharaPOS inavyotumia cookie na teknolojia zinazofanana kwenye tovuti na programu yetu. Inapaswa kusomwa pamoja na <a href="/privacy">Sera yetu ya Faragha</a>.'}>This Cookie Policy explains how BiasharaPOS uses cookies and similar technologies on our website and application. It should be read together with our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

  <h2 data-en="What are cookies?" data-sw="Cookie ni nini?">What are cookies?</h2>
  <p data-en="Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. We also use similar technologies such as your browser’s local storage to remember your preferences." data-sw="Cookie ni faili ndogo za maandishi zinazohifadhiwa kwenye kifaa chako unapotembelea tovuti. Pia tunatumia teknolojia zinazofanana kama hifadhi ya ndani ya kivinjari chako kukumbuka mapendeleo yako.">Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. We also use similar technologies such as your browser’s local storage to remember your preferences.</p>

  <h2 data-en="How we use them" data-sw="Jinsi tunavyozitumia">How we use them</h2>
  <ul>
    <li data-en="Essential — keeping you signed in and the application working as expected." data-sw="Muhimu — kukuweka umeingia na programu ikifanya kazi kama inavyotarajiwa.">Essential — keeping you signed in and the application working as expected.</li>
    <li data-en="Preferences — remembering your language choice (English or Swahili) via local storage." data-sw="Mapendeleo — kukumbuka chaguo lako la lugha (Kiingereza au Kiswahili) kupitia hifadhi ya ndani.">Preferences — remembering your language choice (English or Swahili) via local storage.</li>
    <li data-en="Analytics — Google Analytics helps us understand how the site is used so we can improve it." data-sw="Takwimu — Google Analytics inatusaidia kuelewa jinsi tovuti inavyotumika ili tuiboreshe.">Analytics — Google Analytics helps us understand how the site is used so we can improve it.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 data-en="Third-party cookies" data-sw="Cookie za watu wengine">Third-party cookies</h2>
  <p data-en="We use Google Analytics to collect aggregated, anonymous usage statistics. These third-party services set their own cookies, governed by their own privacy policies." data-sw="Tunatumia Google Analytics kukusanya takwimu za matumizi zilizojumlishwa na zisizo na utambulisho. Huduma hizi za watu wengine huweka cookie zao wenyewe, zinazotawaliwa na sera zao za faragha.">We use Google Analytics to collect aggregated, anonymous usage statistics. These third-party services set their own cookies, governed by their own privacy policies.</p>

  <h2 data-en="Managing cookies" data-sw="Kudhibiti cookie">Managing cookies</h2>
  <p data-en="You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings at any time. Blocking essential cookies may affect how the Service works. Clearing your browser storage will reset your saved language preference." data-sw="Unaweza kudhibiti au kufuta cookie kupitia mipangilio ya kivinjari chako wakati wowote. Kuzuia cookie muhimu kunaweza kuathiri jinsi Huduma inavyofanya kazi. Kufuta hifadhi ya kivinjari chako kutaweka upya pendeleo lako la lugha lililohifadhiwa.">You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings at any time. Blocking essential cookies may affect how the Service works. Clearing your browser storage will reset your saved language preference.</p>

  <h2 data-en="Contact us" data-sw="Wasiliana nasi">Contact us</h2>
